        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 7 at 3:20PM CDT by NWS Bismarck ND</headline>
        <description>At 320 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 7
miles southeast of Prairie Knights Resort, or 15 miles west of
Linton, moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts of 50 to 55 mph and half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Linton, Westfield, and Beaver Bay Recreation Area.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
